h more accuracy. Whereas the first two defects are\nattractive for the vortices, the third type is repulsive for them, being needed\nseveral vortices penetrated in the superconducting matrix to have vortices\npenetrated into it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 17:37:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
