at seismic speed. Furthermore, shear strength weakening associated\nwith rapid self-pressurization of pore-fluid can account for the slip-fracture\nenergy scaling observed for large earthquakes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 19:54:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
